<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.4.8">
<l>uṇṇātu veṅkūṟṟa mōvātu pāvaṅkaḷ cērā mēlai</l>
<l>viṇṇōrum maṇṇōrum vantiṟaiñcum meṉtaḷirpō laṭiyi ṉāṉai</l>
<l>paṇṇāra vaṇṭiyampum paimpoḻilcūḻ taṇcēṟai yammāṉ ṟaṉṉai</l>
<l>kaṇṇārak kaṇṭurukik kaiyārat toḻuvāraik karutuṅ kālē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Cruel death will not consume [you]; unending misfortune will not reach [you],</l>
<l>When [you] think of those who worship profusely, melting,</l>
<l rend="indent">seeing until their eyes fill</l>
<l>The lord of cool Cēṟai, encircled by verdant groves</l>
<l rend="indent">where melodies of bees resonate profusely,</l>
<l>The one with tender bud-like feet where those of heaven above</l>
<l rend="indent">and those of earth come and bow.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
